text: Mainstockheim is a municipality in Kitzingen in Bavaria in Germany. It is famous for its choir, the Choir of Mainstockheim. Since 2021, Mainstockheim has been a significant site for the study of dendrochronology after fossils of what are potentially the most ancient trees in Germany were found in its forests. ==References== Category:Kitzingen (district)
